data.eml:eml: Southern high latitude squat lobsters II: description of Uroptychus macquariae sp. nov. from Macquarie Ridge

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Schnabel, Kareen E., Burghardt, Ingo, Ahyong, Shane T. (2017): Southern high latitude squat lobsters II: description of Uroptychus macquariae sp. nov. from Macquarie Ridge. Zootaxa 4353 (2): 327-338, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4353.2.4
